name: Rustic wood wildlife tags
description:
Our rustic wood wildlife tags with burnt edges are crafted by hand in the Pacific Northwest.

The set of 12 circle tags includes
3 deer
3 birds
3 rabbits
3 owls

Each tag comes with a natural jute tie. If you would like a deep red
jute tie, simply select the option box. 

The animals are stamped in deep brown and the edges on both sides
of the tags are burnt.

These can be hung on a rustic Christmas tree as ornaments and look wonderful. We did this last Christmas and loved the look. 

They can also be tied along a ribbon or section of jute to make a banner.

name: Red Bird 1
description:
Christmas is the perfect season for red birds.

We can't decide if this little wood bird is primitive, country, modern or classic. Not that it matters much.

Barn red is the color of this hand painted bird perched on a warm pine green base. 

Add this simple, lovely bird at Christmas or any time of the year.
It will make you happy.

Bird measurements:
8 inches tall
8 inches wide

name: 12 wood heart gift tags with burnt edges
description:
Our hand crafted birch wood gift tags are made with love in the Pacific Northwest.

These natural tags are a lovely touch for gifts. They are perfect for a rustic or Scandanavian Christmas tree.

We use these tags on mason jars as hang tags in the cupboard. 

Guests at a woodland wedding may enjoy writing a wish for the bride and groom. Simply hang the wishes on a mossy branch for a bit of magic.

Each tag includes a natural hemp cord tie.

Tags measure  2-3/8" x 1-3/4" x 1/16" each

name: blue bird 2
description:
This sweet wooden bird is perched on her whitewashed base hoping to live with someone who really loves birds and beach cottages.

Bookshelves, window sills and serene bedrooms are all good placed
for this little bird to settle in.

Our bird is painted in a mid range aqua with a whitewashed base.

Bird measurements:
6 and a bit tall
9 inches wide

name: Rustic Chicken Wire Basket with Birds
description:
We love this sweet, rustic metal basket with chicken wire as it's base. Sometimes something can be so perfect in it's imperfection. Kind of like life, really.

Wire can be added to the topmost metal rim for hanging. It fits a small plant pot perfectly and looks wonderful hung in the garden.


basket measurements:
8.5 inches wide at top circle
6 inches wide at base
4.5 inches tall not including the birds

The dried oranges shown are not included.
